#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Mutant Insects"
msgstr "变异昆虫"

#. ~ Description for Mutant Insects
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Expands giant insects, eggs, larva.  Adds new types.  Insects evolve into "
"mega-sized insects.  Some larva are tameable.  Eggs can be modified with "
"mutagen."
msgstr "扩展巨型昆虫、卵、幼虫。添加新类型。昆虫进化为巨型尺寸。部分幼虫可驯服。卵可通过诱变剂改造。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "small bug"
msgid_plural "small bugs"
msgstr[0] "小型虫类"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'small bug'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "A gross bug about the size of rat.  Maybe immature."
msgstr "一只约老鼠大小的恶心虫子。可能尚未成熟。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "large bug"
msgid_plural "large bugs"
msgstr[0] "大型虫类"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large bug'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "A gross bug the size of a dog."
msgstr "一只狗大小的恶心虫子。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "giant bug"
msgid_plural "giant bugs"
msgstr[0] "巨型虫类"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant bug'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "A gigantic bug the size of a dog."
msgstr "一只狗大小的巨大虫子。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant bug'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "An enormous bug the size of a cow or horse."
msgstr "一只牛或马大小的庞大虫子。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "small larva"
msgid_plural "small larvas"
msgstr[0] "小型幼虫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'small larva'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "A gross worm the size of rat."
msgstr "一条老鼠大小的恶心蠕虫。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "large larva"
msgid_plural "large larvas"
msgstr[0] "大型幼虫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large larva'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "A gross worm the size of a dog."
msgstr "一条狗大小的恶心蠕虫。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "giant acidic ant"
msgid_plural "giant acidic ants"
msgstr[0] "巨型酸蚁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant acidic ant'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"A monstrous brown ant the size of a human.  Glistening liquid periodically "
"drips from its swollen abdomen."
msgstr "一只人类大小的恐怖棕色蚂蚁。闪亮的液体从其肿胀的腹部周期性滴落。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "giant acidic ant queen"
msgid_plural "giant acidic ant queens"
msgstr[0] "巨型酸蚁后"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant acidic ant queen'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"An enormous brown ant the size of a cow.  Its orifice seems developed only "
"for egg-laying rather than spraying acid."
msgstr "一只牛大小的庞大棕色蚂蚁。其口器似乎仅用于产卵而非喷射酸液。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "giant acidic ant soldier"
msgid_plural "giant acidic ant soldiers"
msgstr[0] "巨型酸蚁兵蚁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant acidic ant soldier'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"A monstrous wolly brown ant the size of an adult human.  Glistening liquid "
"periodically drips from its swollen abdomen and it bears a pair of scythe "
"like mandibles."
msgstr "一只成年人类大小的恐怖毛茸棕色蚂蚁。闪亮的液体从其肿胀的腹部周期性滴落，并长有一对镰刀状颚。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "mega acid ant"
msgid_plural "mega acid ants"
msgstr[0] "超级酸蚁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mega acid ant'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"A monstrous woolly brown ant the size of a water buffalo.  Glistening liquid"
" periodically drips from its swollen abdomen and it bears a pair of scythe "
"like mandibles."
msgstr "一只水牛大小的恐怖毛茸棕色蚂蚁。闪亮的液体从其肿胀的腹部周期性滴落，并长有一对镰刀状颚。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "giant acidic ant larva"
msgid_plural "giant acidic ant larvae"
msgstr[0] "巨型酸液蚁幼虫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant acidic ant larva', 'str_pl': 'giant acidic
#. ant larvae'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"A yellow grub the size of a dog.  It squirms and oozes gelatinous fluids."
msgstr "一条狗那么大的黄色蛆虫。它蠕动着，渗出凝胶状液体。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"A yellow grub the size of a dog.  It squirms and oozes gelatinous fluids.  "
"This one seems unusually friendly."
msgstr "一条狗那么大的黄色蛆虫。它蠕动着，渗出凝胶状液体。这只似乎异常友好。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "giant ant"
msgid_plural "giant ants"
msgstr[0] "巨型蚂蚁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant ant'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"An enormous red ant the size of a full grown human.  It possesses a pair of "
"wriggling antennae and vicious-looking mandibles."
msgstr "一只成年人类大小的巨大红蚁。它长有一对蠕动的触角和看起来凶恶的大颚。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "giant ant queen"
msgid_plural "giant ant queens"
msgstr[0] "巨型蚁后"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant ant queen'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"A colossal red ant the size of a cow.  It moves slowly and deliberately, "
"tending to nearby eggs and continually laying more."
msgstr "一头牛那么大的庞然红蚁。它缓慢而谨慎地移动，照料附近的卵并持续产下更多。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "giant ant soldier"
msgid_plural "giant ant soldiers"
msgstr[0] "巨型兵蚁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant ant soldier'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"A huge and hairy red ant the size of an adult human.  Bulging pincers extend"
" from its jaws."
msgstr "一只成年人类大小的巨大毛茸茸红蚁。其颚部伸出鼓胀的钳子。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "mega ant"
msgid_plural "mega ants"
msgstr[0] "超级蚂蚁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mega ant'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"A monstrous red ant the size of a bison.   Bulging pincers extend from its "
"jaws."
msgstr "一只野牛那么大的恐怖红蚁。其颚部伸出鼓胀的钳子。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "gigantic ant larva"
msgid_plural "gigantic ant larvae"
msgstr[0] "巨型蚁幼虫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gigantic ant larva', 'str_pl': 'gigantic ant
#. larvae'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant wasp larva', 'str_pl': 'giant wasp
#. larvae'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"A pulsating sausage of glistening white flesh, the size of a dog.  On one "
"end is a set of squirming mouth parts."
msgstr "一条狗那么大的脉动香肠状闪亮白色肉体。一端长有一套蠕动的口器。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"A pulsating sausage of glistening white flesh, the size of a dog.  On one "
"end is a set of squirming mouth parts.  THis one seems rather playful."
msgstr "一条狗那么大的脉动香肠状闪亮白色肉体。一端长有一套蠕动的口器。这只似乎相当顽皮。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "giant bee"
msgid_plural "giant bees"
msgstr[0] "巨型蜜蜂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant bee'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"With a stinger the size of a kitchen knife, this dog-sized insect's black "
"and yellow markings warn you to leave it undisturbed."
msgstr "这只狗那么大的昆虫长有厨房刀大小的螫针，其黑黄相间的斑纹警告你不要打扰它。"

#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid "giant queen bee"
msgid_plural "giant queen bees"
msgstr[0] "巨型蜂后"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant queen bee'}
#: .\mutant_insect.json
msgid ""
"A colossal bee the size of a cow.  It moves slowly and deliberately, tending"
